  "Interpreting the sign extension of `(x : BitVec w)` to width `v`\ncomputes `x % 2^v` (where `%` is the balanced mod). See `toInt_signExtend` for a version stated\nin terms of `toInt` instead of `toNat`.\n",
  "kind": "markdown"},
 "detail":
