Resolution of ac_rfl:
{"label": "ac_rfl",
 "kind": 14,
 "documentation":
 {"value":
  "`ac_rfl` proves equalities up to application of an associative and commutative operator.\n```\ninstance : Std.Associative (α := Nat) (.+.) := ⟨Nat.add_assoc⟩\ninstance : Std.Commutative (α := Nat) (.+.) := ⟨Nat.add_comm⟩\n\nexample (a b c d : Nat) : a + b + c + d = d + (b + c) + a := by ac_rfl\n```\n",
  "kind": "markdown"},
 "data": ["file:///completionEmptyBy.lean", 73, 21, 0]}
